summary: WHILE PULLING OUT OF PARKING LOT VEHICLE STARTED TO STALL , HAD TO PUMP GAS PEDAL. THIS CAUSED THE VEHICLE TO LURCH FORWARD WITH A SPUTTERING EFFECT. THOUGHT IT MIGHT STALL OUT. THIS HAS HAPPENED A FEW TIMES, ALSO WHEN I TURN VEHICLE OFF IT WILL NOT START AND THERE IS NO ELECTRICAL OPERATION AT ALL. I'VE FOUND I MUST REMOVE KEY FROM IGNITION BEFORE IT WILL RESTART. THIS INSTANCES HAPPEN AT RANDOM
